{"title":"Visibility","author":{"name":"Maura Stanton"},"publishDate":"2011-10-26","lines":[{"line":"I have no illusions.","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"When I roll towards you at dawn,","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"I can’t see you in the fog.","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"We’ve simply memorized each other.","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"I read a story about a giant","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"who couldn’t see his tiny wife","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"for all the clouds","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"drifting around his huge, sad head.","stanza":1,"number":8},{"line":"He’d stroke the tops of fir trees","stanza":1,"number":9},{"line":"thinking he’d found her hair.","stanza":1,"number":10},{"line":"In another version, his wife","stanza":1,"number":11},{"line":"turned into an egret,","stanza":1,"number":12},{"line":"her strong wings","stanza":1,"number":13},{"line":"brushing her husband’s face;","stanza":1,"number":14},{"line":"then she fell into the sea","stanza":1,"number":15},{"line":"weighted down by his immense tear.","stanza":1,"number":16},{"line":"Let me tell you this:","stanza":1,"number":17},{"line":"I miss your shadow, too,","stanza":1,"number":18},{"line":"but I know it waits above the fog","stanza":1,"number":19},{"line":"black as the shadow of the oak","stanza":1,"number":20},{"line":"you saw in your dream","stanza":1,"number":21},{"line":"when you woke up, almost happy.","stanza":1,"number":22},{"line":"I know our town’s invisible.","stanza":1,"number":23},{"line":"The pilots on the way to Alaska","stanza":1,"number":24},{"line":"think they’re over the sea.","stanza":1,"number":25},{"line":"Even if they glimpsed a light","stanza":1,"number":26},{"line":"through a rift in the clouds","stanza":1,"number":27},{"line":"they’d call it a ship","stanza":1,"number":28},{"line":"loaded with timber for the south.","stanza":1,"number":29},{"line":"Still, I hear those planes.","stanza":1,"number":30},{"line":"Last night on the satellite map","stanza":1,"number":31},{"line":"I saw land without clouds.","stanza":1,"number":32},{"line":"Remember, I groped for your hand.","stanza":1,"number":33},{"line":"Suppose the men go barefoot?","stanza":1,"number":34},{"line":"Suppose the women own fans?","stanza":1,"number":35}]}